{
  "_title": "NR4A3 LBD cryptic Pocket-5 detection over a BioEmu conformational ensemble (metadynamics cross-check)",
  "_method": "BioEmu equilibrium-ensemble frames \u2192 fpocket \u2192 harmonized score-independent Pocket-5 match (fixed lining set 406,407,410,411,412,481,484,485,531,534; jaccard>=0.25, frac_recovered>=0.30, centroid<=8.0 A) \u2192 druggability vs D*=0.53. IDENTICAL scorers to the metad/release ensembles (pocket_tracking + nr4a3_structure).",
